---
layout: layouts/base.njk
title: "HVAC Repair, Furnace & AC Installation — Mississauga & GTA"
description: "Queensway Heating and Cooling — the GTA's trusted HVAC experts. Furnace repair, AC installation, heat pumps, ductless AC, fireplaces, and HRV services. Same-day emergency service. Call now."
---

{# ── HERO ────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────── #}
<section class="hero" aria-label="Welcome">
  <div class="hero__bg" aria-hidden="true">
    <img
      src="/assets/img/hero-home.jpg"
      alt="Queensway Heating and Cooling technician servicing a furnace in a GTA home"
      width="1920" height="960"
      fetchpriority="high"
      decoding="async"
    >
  </div>
  <div class="hero__overlay" aria-hidden="true"></div>
  <div class="hero__content">
    <div class="container">
      <div class="hero__grid">
        <div class="hero__text">
          <h1>The GTA's Trusted Heating &amp; Cooling Experts</h1>
          <p class="hero__sub">Your comfort, guaranteed. Count on Queensway Heating and Cooling for furnace repair, AC installation, and heat pump services in Mississauga, Oakville, Brampton, and the GTA.</p>
          <div class="hero__ctas">
            <a href="tel:{{ site.phonePlain }}" class="btn btn-accent btn-lg" aria-label="Call {{ site.phone }}">
              <svg width="20" height="20" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" aria-hidden="true"><path d="M22 16.92v3a2 2 0 01-2.18 2 19.79 19.79 0 01-8.63-3.07A19.5 19.5 0 013.07 10.8 19.79 19.79 0 01.22 2.18 2 2 0 012.18 0h3a2 2 0 012 1.72c.127.96.361 1.903.7 2.81a2 2 0 01-.45 2.11L6.91 7.91a16 16 0 006.18 6.18l1.27-1.27a2 2 0 012.11-.45c.907.339 1.85.573 2.81.7A2 2 0 0122 16.92z"/></svg>
              Call: {{ site.phone }}
            </a>
            <a href="/quote/" class="btn btn-primary btn-lg">Get a Free Quote</a>
          </div>
        </div>
        {# Right column intentionally empty — breathing space on desktop #}
        <div aria-hidden="true"></div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

{# ── SERVICES INTRO HEADING ──────────────────────────────────────────────── #}
<div class="section-intro">
  <div class="container">
    <h2>Why You'll Love Our Expert Heating &amp; Cooling Services</h2>
    <p>From emergency furnace repair to heat pump installations with thousands in rebates — Queensway delivers honest, reliable HVAC service every time.</p>
  </div>
</div>

